      <section class="w-full" id="builtByDevelopers"><div><div class="tabs-section">
      <div class="tabs-section-inner">
        <div class="tabs-inner">
          <div class="tabs-top">
            <p class="tabs-top-title">Built by developers, for developers</p>
            <p class="tabs-top-description">The document data model maps to how you think and code.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="tabs-middle">
            <div class="tabs-middle-text"><div class="tabs-textblock tab-textblock-active">
            <div class="tabs-textblock-indicator"></div>
            <div class="tabs-textblock-text">
              <p class="tabs-textblock-title">Model</p>
              <div class="tabs-textblock-description-wrapper">
                <p class="tabs-textblock-description">Escape from rigid, tabular data structures with flexible documents that map directly to objects in code. Incorporate nested objects, vector embeddings, geospatial and time-series measurements into a data model optimized for performance, compute cost, and productivity.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
              </div><div class="tabs-textblock">
            <div class="tabs-textblock-indicator"></div>
            <div class="tabs-textblock-text">
              <p class="tabs-textblock-title">Query</p>
              <div class="tabs-textblock-description-wrapper">
                <p class="tabs-textblock-description">Use an expressive, developer-native query API to work with data anyway your application needs. Retrieve and modify documents. Prompt LLMs with semantic search across vectors. Aggregate, transform and analyze your data in place, without having to ETL it to another system</p>
              </div>
            </div>
              </div><div class="tabs-textblock">
            <div class="tabs-textblock-indicator"></div>
            <div class="tabs-textblock-text">
              <p class="tabs-textblock-title">Optimize</p>
              <div class="tabs-textblock-description-wrapper">
                <p class="tabs-textblock-description">Optimize queries, react instantly to database changes, and generate materialized views on-demand. MongoDB makes it easy to receive and process millions of requests per day with no change in performance.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
              </div></div>
          <div class="tabs-middle-codeblock-wrapper"><div class="tabs-middle-codeblock"><div class="tabs-middle-codeblock"><div class="tabs-codeblock-title"><div class="tabs-codeblock-language tabs-codeblock-active-lang" data-poc-trc="doc data Model | 1-to-1">1-to-1</div><div class="tabs-codeblock-language" data-poc-trc="doc data Model | 1-to-Many">1-to-Many</div><div class="tabs-codeblock-language" data-poc-trc="doc data Model | Many-to-Many">Many-to-Many</div></div><div class="tabs-codeblock-body">
                <div class="tabs-codeline-wrapper"> <div class="tabs-code-num">0</div><div class="tabs-code-line tabs-indent-0 cl-comment"> # Option 1: Model one-to-many </div></div>
                <div class="tabs-codeline-wrapper"> <div class="tabs-code-num">1</div><div class="tabs-code-line tabs-indent-0 cl-comment"> # relationships with embedded documents </div></div>
                <div class="tabs-codeline-wrapper"><div class="tabs-code-num">2</div><div class="tabs-code-line tabs-indent-0"> </div></div>
                <div class="tabs-codeline-wrapper"><div class="tabs-code-num">3</div><div class="tabs-code-line tabs-indent-0"> <span class="cl-blue">Order=</span>{</div></div>
                <div class="tabs-codeline-wrapper"><div class="tabs-code-num">4</div><div class="tabs-code-line tabs-indent-1"> <span class="cl-purple">"_id":</span> <span class="cl-yellow">"2934f"</span>, </div></div>
                <div class="tabs-codeline-wrapper"><div class="tabs-code-num">5</div><div class="tabs-code-line tabs-indent-1"> <span class="cl-purple">"salesDate":</span> <span class="cl-yellow">"2022-05-02"</span>, </div></div>
